"Q14","A man falls into a deep sleep with one arm under his head. He finds he is not able to move this arm when he awakens. However, it tingles and pain sensation in the arm is still intact. what is the reason for the loss of motor function without loss of pain sensation is that in the nerves to his arm?","a) B fibers are more susceptible to pressure than A fibers
